f festival music: {{ill|Sawara Hayashi|ja|佐原囃子|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sawara Hayashi|qq=}} and {{ill|Edo Hayashi|ja|江戸囃子|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Edo Hayashi|qq=}}. In the three neighborhoods possessing Edo-style floats of the hoko-dai type, Edo Hayashi is performed, while in the other seven neighborhoods, Sawara Hayashi is featured.
